Returns: The @B_com#google#android#gms#appstate#AppStateManager#StateLoadedResult_E@ if the operation did not result in a conflict, or null otherwise.

ClassDesc: Result of an operation that could potentially generate a state conflict. Note that at most one of getLoadedResult or getConflictResult will ever return a non-null value. In the event of a @B_com#google#android#gms#common#api#CommonStatusCodes#INTERRUPTED_E@ status, both getLoadedResult and getConflictResult will return null.
